property.value: function onReceiveOSC(message) local text = message[2][1].value self.values.text = text:gsub("#", "█") return true end

local map = { ["!"] = "➡", }
local lastValue = ""
function onReceiveOSC(msg) local newValue = msg[2][1].value
if newValue == lastValue then return true end
lastValue = newValue
local editedValue = newValue
for k,v in pairs(map) do editedValue = editedValue:gsub(k, v) end
self.values.text = editedValue return true end
